=============================================
DO THE FOLLOWINGS TO TEST CLIENT-SERVER-KUANG:


I) ON SERVER MACHINE
  1/ file kuang, comment out the last line, if 
     don't want this server to send request to another server: 
	#./part2

  2/ File init_kuang can have no goal initially

II) ON CLIENT MACHINE
  1/ file kuang: must have 
 	./part2

  2/ create ~user/.rhosts file
	Example: ~userA/.rhosts
			machine1 userA
			machine1 userB
			machine2 userC

  3/ File init_kuang must have goal initially


III) TO RUN:
  1/ On server site, type:
	./k_server &

  2/ On client site, type:
	./kuang

IV) RESULTS:

  See file Success 

===================================================
Kuang intergrated in tara.

TO RUN: 
 1/ Follow steps I to III above
 2/ Then type
 	./tiger

RESULT:
 See file security.report....
